Starting from 29th of July, 2020 restaurants, bars and cafes are open but with the following restrictions: 
-tables are arranged to ensure a distance of at least 1.5 meters between them; 
-a maximum of 10 people per table is authorized; 
-only table seats are allowed; each customer must sit at his own table; 
-the wearing of a mask by room and kitchen staff is mandatory; 
